## Retrieve a storage

> REQUEST

```shell
curl -X GET \
  <%= config[:endpoint] %>/media/storage \
  -H 'Authorization: <%= config[:token] %>' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
    "appId": "<%= config[:app_id] %>",
    "id": "<%= config[:storage_retrieve_id] %>"
}'
```

```ruby
require "json"

Uiza.app_id = "<%= config[:app_id] %>"
Uiza.authorization = "<%= config[:token] %>"

begin
  storage = Uiza::Storage.retrieve "<%= config[:storage_retrieve_id] %>"
